  "event_preview": "Fuji Speedway is a 4.563 km permanent road course at the foot of Mount Fuji in Oyama, Shizuoka Prefecture. The July 2026 visit is a triple-header: Round 6 on Saturday 18 July, the rescheduled Round 3 race from Autopolis (cancelled after qualifying on 25 April) as the second race of the weekend, then Round 7 on Sunday 19 July. Autopolis qualifying points (3/2/1) were already awarded in the Round 3 standings column; race points for Round 3 will be added here when that race is run. Each race is scheduled for 37 laps (177.7 km) with the usual mandatory pit window.",
